content: I'm glad you're excited about the Rock Café and the true crime podcasts. Speaking of true crime podcasts, I was just talking to my friend Rachel about them during our video call earlier this month. She's a big fan of them too. Anyway, back to Route 66 - do you think I could get some recommendations for accommodations along the route? I'm thinking of staying in some vintage motels or roadside inns to really get into the spirit of the trip.
